								</a>
							</div>
						</div>
						// 링크 그룹 1
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-base font-medium text-white">서비스</h3>
							<ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
								<li><a href="/services/ai-study" class="text-base text-gray-400 hover:text-white">AI 공부 도우미</a></li>
								<li><a href="/services/diary" class="text-base text-gray-400 hover:text-white">나만의 일기장</a></li>
								<li><a href="/services/todo" class="text-base text-gray-400 hover:text-white">나만의 TODO 앱</a></li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						// 링크 그룹 2
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-base font-medium text-white">회사 정보</h3>
							<ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
								<li><a href="/about" class="text-base text-gray-400 hover:text-white">소개</a></li>
								<li><a href="/team" class="text-base text-gray-400 hover:text-white">팀</a></li>
								<li><a href="/blog" class="text-base text-gray-400 hover:text-white">블로그</a></li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						// 링크 그룹 3
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-base font-medium text-white">지원</h3>
							<ul class="mt-4 space-y-2">
								<li><a href="/contact" class="text-base text-gray-400 hover:text-white">문의하기</a></li>
